issues.title: TypeError when extracting all entries
issues.body:


issue_comments.body:
It looks like the problem is actually with the table datasets, which are extensible but have a chunk size larger than their length, usually. My solution is to copy all datasets, squeezing out empty dims when necessary, make them non-extensible, and thereby fix the chunk values in the process. This should also help to optimize the files for read performance.

I'm not going to fix the problem in the 1.1 conversion function, because I can't find any earlier files to test it on.
